23
00:02:20,095 --> 00:02:22,490
♪ You won't really ♪

24
00:02:22,526 --> 00:02:24,365
♪ Fall in love ♪

25
00:02:24,399 --> 00:02:28,598
♪ 'Cause you can't
take the chance ♪

26
00:02:28,634 --> 00:02:32,700
♪ So be honest with yourself ♪

27
00:02:32,736 --> 00:02:37,408
♪ Don't try to fake romance ♪

28
00:02:37,443 --> 00:02:40,083
♪ Yes, the good life ♪

29
00:02:40,119 --> 00:02:41,844
- BECCA: See you, sweetheart.
- BRADY: Bye, Mom.

30
00:02:41,878 --> 00:02:45,581
♪ To be free
and explore the unknown ♪

31
00:02:45,616 --> 00:02:48,188
♪ Like the heartaches ♪

32
00:02:48,224 --> 00:02:50,288
