33
00:02:50,324 --> 00:02:53,296
♪ Face them alone ♪

34
00:02:54,735 --> 00:02:56,760
♪ Please remember ♪

35
00:02:56,795 --> 00:02:58,869
- ♪ I still want you ♪
- (groaning)

36
00:02:58,905 --> 00:03:01,062
- (gunshot)
- ♪ And in case ♪

37
00:03:01,098 --> 00:03:04,071
- ♪ You wonder why ♪
- (grunting and groaning)

38
00:03:04,106 --> 00:03:06,309
♪ Well, just wake up ♪

39
00:03:07,637 --> 00:03:10,842
♪ Well, just wake up ♪

40
00:03:12,181 --> 00:03:14,147
♪ Well, just wake up ♪

41
00:03:14,183 --> 00:03:16,950
♪ Kiss that good life ♪

42
00:03:16,986 --> 00:03:22,158
