56
00:04:38,837 --> 00:04:41,138
Sammy? Fruit, please.

57
00:04:41,175 --> 00:04:43,298
- Okey dokey.
- BECCA: Brady, eat the protein.

58
00:04:43,335 --> 00:04:44,972
I am good.

59
00:04:45,008 --> 00:04:46,207
(Becca scoffs)

60
00:04:46,243 --> 00:04:47,904
BECCA:
Clean your plate, please.

61
