- Hey, that's Dad's.
- BRADY: Is he even home?

62
00:04:50,015 --> 00:04:51,145
- Bye, Lasagna.
- (Lasagna meows)

63
00:04:51,181 --> 00:04:52,917
Hey, cut him some slack, okay?

64
00:04:52,952 --> 00:04:54,311
- Always.
- (horn honking outside)

65
00:04:54,347 --> 00:04:55,710
BECCA:
Hold up.

66
00:04:55,746 --> 00:04:57,815
- I love you.
- Okay. Love you.

67
00:04:57,849 --> 00:04:59,421
- Hey, babe.
- SAMMY: My friends are here.

68
00:04:59,457 --> 00:05:02,352
- Okay. Uh, have a nice...
- (horn honks outside)

69
00:05:02,387 --> 00:05:04,159
(sighs) Hey, hon?

70
00:05:04,193 --> 00:05:05,820
I, uh, slept in the basement

71
00:05:05,856 --> 00:05:07,760
- so I wouldn't wake you.
- Uh-huh.

72
00:05:07,796 --> 00:05:11,027
Okay, where's Brady?
I want to hear about the game.

73
00:05:12,462 --> 00:05:15,239
Well, uh...

74
00:05:15,275 --> 00:05:18,534
the other team was kind of,
you know, physical.

75
00:05:18,570 --> 00:05:20,741
- Yeah?
- So he, um...

76
00:05:21,873 --> 00:05:24,546
I'll let him tell you.
Very busy day.

77
00:05:24,582 --> 00:05:28,553
I've got three showings
and one confirmed sale.

78
00:05:28,589 --> 00:05:30,053
And, uh...

79
00:05:30,087 --> 00:05:31,847
Oh. Brady stole your coffee.

80
00:05:31,883 --> 00:05:33,354
You're gonna have to make
some more.

81
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:35,151
- Well, we had...
- Hutch, you're bleeding.

82
00:05:36,592 --> 00:05:38,390
- All right, we should, uh...
- (door closes)

83
00:05:38,425 --> 00:05:40,890
(clears throat, sighs)

84
00:05:40,925 --> 00:05:43,096
(truck backup alarm
