85
00:05:43,130 --> 00:05:44,633
Oh, damn it.

86
00:05:44,669 --> 00:05:46,096
Hey!

87
00:05:47,101 --> 00:05:48,570
Hey, buddy.

88
00:05:49,503 --> 00:05:50,976
- Hey, man.
- BRADY: Bye, Mom.

89
00:05:51,010 --> 00:05:52,440
- SAMMY: Bye, Mom.
- HUTCH: Yeah.

90
00:05:52,476 --> 00:05:54,609
- BECCA: Have a great day!
- BRADY: All right.

91
00:05:56,645 --> 00:05:58,215
- SAMMY: Hey, guys.
- FRIEND: Hi, Sammy.

92
00:05:58,252 --> 00:05:59,746
- HUTCH: Hey, you...
- FRIEND: Love your shoes.

93
00:05:59,781 --> 00:06:01,251
- BRADY: Morning.
- FRIEND 2: Oh, love yours, too.

94
00:06:01,286 --> 00:06:02,481
- SAMMY: Yours, too.
- FRIEND 2: Thank you.

95
00:06:02,515 --> 00:06:04,147
Yeah, I got 'em from the mall.

96
00:06:04,181 --> 00:06:05,320
FRIEND 1: Are you going
anywhere for summer break?

97
00:06:05,354 --> 00:06:06,750
FRIEND 2:
Yeah, I'm going bowling.

98
00:06:06,786 --> 00:06:08,854
(conversation continues
indistinctly)

99
00:06:12,193 --> 00:06:13,661
BECCA:
Hutch?

100
00:06:15,032 --> 00:06:16,335
What's up, hon?

101
00:06:17,330 --> 00:06:19,130
You know...

102
00:06:19,166 --> 00:06:20,702
(scoffs)

103
00:06:22,166 --> 00:06:25,803
Uh, summer break's
in just a few days, and...

104
00:06:25,839 --> 00:06:28,572
We should do something
as a family. Yeah.

105
00:06:28,608 --> 00:06:31,142
I, uh... I'll make a plan.

106
00:06:31,176 --> 00:06:33,976
Today I'll make a plan,
and, uh, I'll tell you tonight.

107
00:06:34,010 --> 00:06:35,945
- At dinner. I'll make lasagna.
- (sighs)

108
00:06:35,981 --> 00:06:38,585
- Sure, Hutch. (laughs)
- No, I can do it. I...

109
00:06:38,619 --> 00:06:41,024
I have... I have
one assignment today.

110
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:44,688
Uh, but then tonight you'll see,

111
00:06:44,722 --> 00:06:47,157
uh, the whole thing planned out.

112
00:06:56,402 --> 00:06:58,068
What's going on?

113
00:07:00,176 --> 00:07:01,712
(Becca sighs)

114
00:07:01,748 --> 00:07:03,140
Never mind.

115
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:10,080
♪ ♪

116
00:07:22,935 --> 00:07:24,359
(elevator bell dings)

117
00:07:26,433 --> 00:07:28,604
(quiet chatter)

118
00:07:42,383 --> 00:07:44,279
(elevator bell dings)

119
00:07:55,363 --> 00:07:57,193
(takes deep breath)

120
00:07:59,565 --> 00:08:01,704
(jazzy melody playing)

121
00:08:13,248 --> 00:08:14,717
There you are.

122
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,664
Looks like your day went long.

123
00:08:29,728 --> 00:08:32,192
It was a bit more... big.

124
00:08:32,229 --> 00:08:35,133
Bit more than the prep
said it would be.

125
00:08:36,602 --> 00:08:38,642
The data card.

126
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:42,008
(clears throat)

127
00:08:44,608 --> 00:08:46,078
(sighs)

128
00:08:47,946 --> 00:08:50,651
It was a straightforward
snatch, Hutch.

129
00:08:50,686 --> 00:08:54,526
It started as
a straightforward snatch.

130
00:08:55,527 --> 00:08:58,562
You guys having fun
at the convention?

131
00:08:58,598 --> 00:09:02,456
Asshole, we're not here
for the fucking convention.

132
00:09:04,028 --> 00:09:06,094
- (grunting, yelling)
- (two gunshots)

133
00:09:06,129 --> 00:09:08,264
