- (whimpering)

134
00:09:09,107 --> 00:09:10,139
(grunts, coughs)

135
00:09:10,175 --> 00:09:12,543
(grunting and groaning)

136
00:09:16,047 --> 00:09:17,208
(yells in pain)

137
00:09:18,378 --> 00:09:19,650
Oh, my.

138
00:09:35,565 --> 00:09:37,195
Please! Someone help us.
(stammers)

139
00:09:37,229 --> 00:09:40,132
AUTOMATED VOICE: An operator
will assist you shortly.

140
00:09:42,138 --> 00:09:44,169
(grunting)

141
00:09:46,242 --> 00:09:48,209
(cries out)

142
00:09:48,243 --> 00:09:50,009
(crunching)

143
00:09:51,676 --> 00:09:53,079
(whimpering)

144
00:09:57,655 --> 00:09:59,921
- (breathing heavily)
- (others groaning)

145
