Right. Straightforward snatch.

149
00:10:31,525 --> 00:10:34,925
Yeah. Until the Corsicans
showed up with Uzis.

150
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,189
♪ ♪

151
00:10:40,463 --> 00:10:43,128
Wait. No, they had MP7s.

152
00:10:52,939 --> 00:10:54,777
- (explosion booms)
- (man yells)

153
00:10:55,773 --> 00:10:56,913
Corsicans, huh?

154
00:10:56,950 --> 00:10:58,540
With MP7s.

155
00:10:59,551 --> 00:11:01,210
Well, we always suspected
there might be

156
00:11:01,244 --> 00:11:03,448
another interested party
in the mix.

157
00:11:03,483 --> 00:11:05,315
Only one?

158
00:11:06,554 --> 00:11:08,959
