161
00:11:14,397 --> 00:11:16,161
(tires squealing)

162
00:11:19,939 --> 00:11:21,672
(sighs)

163
00:11:25,343 --> 00:11:26,940
(electrical crackling)

164
00:11:26,977 --> 00:11:29,406
