170
00:11:42,523 --> 00:11:44,585
(song resumes)

171
00:11:50,795 --> 00:11:51,969
(song stops)

172
00:11:52,003 --> 00:11:53,234
Oh, my.

173
00:11:53,268 --> 00:11:54,565
Yeah.

174
00:11:54,599 --> 00:11:55,930
Oh, my.

175
00:11:55,965 --> 00:11:58,065
(tablet beeping)

176
00:11:58,100 --> 00:12:00,139
(trilling, beeping)

177
00:12:03,975 --> 00:12:05,810
Well, I'd say it was worth it.

178
00:12:05,844 --> 00:12:07,509
