182
00:12:20,363 --> 00:12:21,623
(snaps fingers)

183
00:12:25,065 --> 00:12:27,738
- Your next mission.
- (Hutch sighs)

184
00:12:29,142 --> 00:12:31,171
(folder rustling)

185
00:12:33,341 --> 00:12:34,536
I can't.

186
00:12:37,181 --> 00:12:38,647
Hutch...

187
00:12:38,684 --> 00:12:40,474
I'm trying to help you
pay off a debt.

188
00:12:40,509 --> 00:12:44,150
One we very graciously paid
on your behalf

189
00:12:44,185 --> 00:12:47,384
when you burnt all
the Russian's stack of money.

190
00:12:52,022 --> 00:12:53,829
At the rate you're going,

191
00:12:53,864 --> 00:12:56,932
you'll have paid off
the obshchak by spring.

192
00:12:57,929 --> 00:13:00,100
Gonna take a va...

193
00:13:01,229 --> 00:13:03,666
I'm gonna take a break.

194
00:13:03,703 --> 00:13:05,743
♪ ♪

195
00:13:17,551 --> 00:13:19,054
Good luck.

196
00:13:22,724 --> 00:13:24,821
