202
00:13:53,282 --> 00:13:55,926
(Hutch groaning softly)

203
00:14:01,728 --> 00:14:03,493
(body thuds)

204
00:14:04,665 --> 00:14:06,397
(chuckles)

205
00:14:10,001 --> 00:14:11,773
Wild times await.

206
00:14:11,809 --> 00:14:14,238
This summer,
drive to Plummerville,

207
00:14:14,272 --> 00:14:16,109
