for summer fun.

209
00:14:19,849 --> 00:14:21,908
(laughs)
With the majestic midway.

210
00:14:21,945 --> 00:14:23,610
Hey!

211
00:14:23,647 --> 00:14:26,949
And to top it off,
America's first and finest

212
00:14:26,984 --> 00:14:30,394
