213
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:32,554
You kids having summer fun?

214
00:14:32,589 --> 00:14:35,258
BOTH: Sure are,
Mr. Wild Bill... (screaming)

215
00:14:35,295 --> 00:14:39,600
WILD BILL:
Slides for miles and miles!

216
00:14:39,637 --> 00:14:43,129
Because Plummerville is...

217
00:14:43,166 --> 00:14:44,604
