220
00:14:51,482 --> 00:14:53,512
Again and again...

221
00:14:53,548 --> 00:14:55,316
(chuckles)

222
00:14:55,352 --> 00:14:56,653
Yeah.

223
00:14:56,689 --> 00:14:58,411
Um, that commercial
is really old.

224
00:14:58,446 --> 00:15:00,416
Are you sure it's still a place?

225
00:15:00,451 --> 00:15:01,987
Yeah, it's all there.
I-I checked. It's...

226
00:15:02,022 --> 00:15:03,594
The hotel and the water park,

227
00:15:03,629 --> 00:15:06,461
uh, the duck boats
and the midway.

228
00:15:06,498 --> 00:15:07,930
What's a duck boat?

229
00:15:07,964 --> 00:15:11,292
It's, um... it's like
a bus that floats.

230
00:15:11,328 --> 00:15:13,095
Uh, it's a military vehicle.

231
00:15:13,131 --> 00:15:14,695
Grandpa will love it.

232
00:15:14,730 --> 00:15:17,365
- We're bringing Grandpa?
- We're bringing Grandpa?

233
00:15:17,401 --> 00:15:19,040
- Yeah, of course.
- (Brady sighs)

234
00:15:19,075 --> 00:15:22,112
You know what?
Um, I volunteer to stay home.

235
00:15:22,147 --> 00:15:24,613
- Yeah, that's not gonna happen.
- HUTCH: Yeah, Brady, listen.

236
00:15:24,650 --> 00:15:26,339
This is gonna be the most fu...

237
00:15:26,376 --> 00:15:27,743
What happened to your eye?

238
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,650
Somebody fouled me at the game.

239
00:15:31,685 --> 00:15:33,488
What game?

240
00:15:33,525 --> 00:15:35,148
The one you missed.

241
00:15:35,185 --> 00:15:36,551
You're right.

242
00:15:36,586 --> 00:15:37,889
We do need to spend
more time together

243
00:15:37,925 --> 00:15:39,723
- as a family.
- Yeah.

244
00:15:39,758 --> 00:15:41,829
This is one of those places
you went when you were a kid.

245
00:15:41,863 --> 00:15:43,391
Okay, that makes it sound like

246
00:15:43,426 --> 00:15:45,062
I went to a lot of places, okay?

247
00:15:45,098 --> 00:15:47,064
Dad took us on one vacation.

248
00:15:47,099 --> 00:15:49,503
One. To Plummerville.

249
00:15:49,538 --> 00:15:52,410
♪ ♪

250
00:15:52,445 --> 00:15:55,138
(clears throat) Listen.

251
00:15:55,173 --> 00:15:58,047
In life, when times get tough,

252
00:15:58,084 --> 00:16:02,652
