to carry you through,

253
00:16:02,686 --> 00:16:04,378
and I just want to show you guys

254
00:16:04,413 --> 00:16:06,383
the place that made me happiest.

255
00:16:06,417 --> 00:16:08,316
You know,
make some memories for you.

256
00:16:08,353 --> 00:16:09,924
Would you let me
do that, please?

257
00:16:09,959 --> 00:16:12,392
- (snickers)
- (Lasagna meowing)

258
00:16:13,690 --> 00:16:15,892
- Well, hello, Lasagna.
- (Hutch chuckling)

259
00:16:15,926 --> 00:16:18,666
Okay.

260
00:16:18,701 --> 00:16:20,030
All right, Hutch. Sure.

261
00:16:20,065 --> 00:16:21,431
- Really?
- Yeah.

262
00:16:21,466 --> 00:16:23,663
