600
00:30:36,886 --> 00:30:38,421
I'm sorry.

601
00:30:38,456 --> 00:30:40,587
You just had to bring
that other side of you?

602
00:30:40,623 --> 00:30:43,900
Brady's already aggressive,
and do you know why?

603
00:30:45,501 --> 00:30:46,901
It's because of you.

604
00:30:46,936 --> 00:30:50,803
Because he is watching you
and what you do.

605
00:30:50,837 --> 00:30:52,470
Look, I lost it, all right?

606
00:30:52,507 --> 00:30:54,277
It's over.

607
00:30:54,313 --> 00:30:56,275
What's in the workbag?

608
00:30:58,346 --> 00:31:00,547
What?

609
00:31:00,583 --> 00:31:02,376
The black bag, Hutch.

610
00:31:02,412 --> 00:31:04,046
- You've been trying to hide it.
- Listen.

611
00:31:04,081 --> 00:31:05,321
Okay, so what's in it?

612
00:31:05,356 --> 00:31:07,490
I'm not here for...

613
00:31:07,526 --> 00:31:09,293
