- Yeah.

614
00:31:09,327 --> 00:31:10,784
And I meant what I said.

615
00:31:11,795 --> 00:31:14,161
BECCA:
Yeah, I remember that promise.

616
00:31:21,469 --> 00:31:22,873
Wine?

617
00:31:23,969 --> 00:31:26,670
It's not just any wine.

618
00:31:26,706 --> 00:31:29,246
♪ ♪

619
00:31:29,280 --> 00:31:31,807
It's from Puglia.

620
00:31:31,844 --> 00:31:33,312
Where we met.

621
00:31:34,318 --> 00:31:36,182
And the year.

622
00:31:43,823 --> 00:31:45,687
(Becca crying)

623
00:31:47,199 --> 00:31:49,162
I'm sorry.

624
00:31:51,535 --> 00:31:53,960
Where'd you find this?

625
00:31:53,996 --> 00:31:55,799
Um, eBay.

626
00:31:55,835 --> 00:31:58,034
- eBay?
- Yeah.

627
00:31:58,068 --> 00:31:59,672
Wait, so you ordered it?

628
00:31:59,708 --> 00:32:02,506
